task.summary:
Added 
performsTraceFunction = ( idTrace : Int, thisRegister : QReg) => {  }
In QReg : useTraceFunction to set, or resetTraceFunction. If set this will call the callback for each step of trace, and provides the step # (as an Int - 0 = start, -1 = end) : idTrace, and thisRegister as a ref to the current register.

